column5: I'm looking for a map chip that covers SE Lac Seul. I have a Humminbird 999 HD SI. I can't find any details online so am wondering if there is anything decent worth dropping $200 or more?

Navionics North (check to confirm Lac Seul is indeed on the chip. I have Lac Seul on mine, but others have told me it is not on theirs).Navionics Canada.Both have basic depth contours same as paper maps that readily available.
Navionics North Chip does have Lac Seul on it. RBF

Where are you going on Lac Seul? I've got a pretty good area mapped from saving sonar logs and using autochart, around the lodge we've been going to for years. I just keep adding a little more each year we go up.
Deception Bay to Mahkwa Lodge? Have anything between those areas? LM
Got quite a bit around Mahkwa. Send me a PM.
